::Cygnar::
       He braces himself against a hull plate as the ship is rocked.  He 
opens a com to Tyrael.  "This is Cygnar.  I'm going out."  He flies back out 
the hole Hydras had made since he was still near the cargo bay before the 
bombs explode.  Spotting Hydras he glares at him and opens fire on his 
exposed backside.

--part1_122.19fe33a1.2af95b93_boundary
